title: 9/23 and no icon
body: I have received my mystery gift from riot but I haven't got the icon for some reason??

replies.body: That reason is gifts are not done being sent out yet.  There are a lot of accounts to gift so it will take some time, but you can stay up to date through our [support banner](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/227317608--Sept-14-Anniversary-gifts-are-currently-being-distributed-You-may-not-receive-them-right-away-so-please-be-patient-).  Hang tight!
